						<p>This is very much damaged and dated <hi rend="bold">Chāḷukya-Vikrama year 12 (= A.D. 1087)</hi> Sūrya-grahaṇa. Only the titles of a Chāḷukya king (name lost) are preserved. It mentions god Sōmēśvara and seems to record a grant of land.</p>						

